        Clause 8 [<span class="italic">Tribunals for considering removal</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-01034'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_247'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-brougham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
