      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0636P0-01056'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_269' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendments Nos. 94 to 97 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0636P0-01057'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_270' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 9 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-01058'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_271'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gareth-williams' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_271' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gareth Williams' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gareth-williams" title="Mr Gareth Williams">Lord Williams of Mostyn</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            This may be a convenient moment for the Committee to adjourn until Thursday at 4 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0636P0-01059'>
        <a name='S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_272'>  </a>
        <blockquote class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <cite class='member author entry-title unmatched-member'>The Deputy Chairman of Committees</cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            The Committee stands adjourned until Thursday 13th June at 4 p.m.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0636P0-01060'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0636P0_20020611_GCR_273' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at twenty-eight minutes past seven o'clock.
      </p>
